	  <h1 class="style1">Welcome</h1>
	<p class="style4">We are pleased you have chosen to browse the website of the Law Office of Fay Blix. </p>
	<p class="style4">Our entire law practice has been devoted to Elder Law (Limited Conservatorship, Special Needs Trusts, Medi-Cal planning) and Estate Planning (Advance Health Care Directives, Wills, Trusts and Probate) for more than twenty years. We pride ourselves in listening to our clients' concerns with empathy and compassion and in applying our professional expertise and experience to craft individualized solutions to our clients' problems. We are committed to practicing law with a heart. We provide this site as a guide to help you journey through the often complicated and confusing emotional, financial and legal issues as a loved one ages or lives with a disability. We also hope this site will help save you time as you search for the right attorney to give you peace of mind. Enjoy your visit and please return often.</p>
